    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "4c1f57ee-5cc7-425e-833d-9fd81982b5b9",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Petal to the Metal",
        "Location": "LOCATION_MUMBAI",
        "PublicId": "113602985240",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Mumbai/scene_mongoose.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository b395fabb-c557-414c-a315-661e1722b1ee).Image",
        "Description": "It seems love can bloom anywhere.\r\rOur client is Abhay: a metal worker working in the slums. He was taken in by Vanya Shah and is grateful for her generosity, only now it has its limits. He has set sights on servant Kiara, and Abhay has grown on her too.\r\rAfter proposing, he asked the royals&apos; permission to make a sunflower brooch for Kiara. However, they denied the union. Fortunately, Abhay disapproved of their decision, placing a hit on them both.\r\rMake the trainyard run rose-red with blood.",
